pr_body:
This is a PR to be approved before the final launch of the p5.js 2021 showcase (launch date Sept 6th), put under review by my mentors KT Duffy (@ktduffyincorperated), Sam Vassor, and Ashley Kang (@kangashley). As a Google Summer of Code student for the Processing Foundation this summer, I continued the development of the p5.js showcase by curating projects based on a theme, adding a difficulty filter, adding social media icons, and taking steps towards increasing accessibility compliance.  

As for the next steps, this website requires updated translations which will be done with the help of the Processing community with the structure that is already set up for them to add and it will also need a transfer of DNS for the showcase.p5js.org from the 2020 showcase to this year.
